sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Django REST API
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant AU as AuditLog
    participant U as User
    participant GL as GeneralLedger
    participant INV as Invoices
    participant PUR as Purchases
    participant INVN as Inventory
    participant REP as Reports

    Note over FE,API: User logs in
    FE->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API->>DB: Validate credentials
    DB-->>API: User data
    API->>AU: Log login event
    API-->>FE: Auth token

    Note over FE,API: User creates a journal entry
    FE->>API: POST /api/general_ledger/journal_entries
    API->>GL: Create JournalEntry, JournalEntryLine
    GL->>DB: Insert journal entry, lines
    DB-->>GL: Success
    GL->>AU: Log create event
    API-->>FE: Journal entry created

    Note over FE,API: User creates an invoice
    FE->>API: POST /api/invoices/
    API->>INV: Create Invoice, InvoiceLine
    INV->>DB: Insert invoice, lines
    DB-->>INV: Success
    INV->>AU: Log create event
    API-->>FE: Invoice created

    Note over FE,API: User creates a purchase order
    FE->>API: POST /api/purchases/orders
    API->>PUR: Create PurchaseOrder, PurchaseOrderLine
    PUR->>DB: Insert purchase order, lines
    DB-->>PUR: Success
    PUR->>AU: Log create event
    API-->>FE: Purchase order created

    Note over FE,API: User adjusts inventory
    FE->>API: POST /api/inventory/adjustments
    API->>INVN: Create InventoryAdjustment
    INVN->>DB: Insert adjustment
    DB-->>INVN: Success
    INVN->>AU: Log adjustment
    API-->>FE: Adjustment created

    Note over FE,API: User generates a financial report
    FE->>API: GET /api/reports/balance_sheet?params
    API->>REP: Generate report
    REP->>DB: Query relevant data
    DB-->>REP: Data
    REP->>AU: Log report generation
    API-->>FE: Report data
